NAME
    gcloud beta ml speech operations - interact with Google Cloud Speech
        operations

SYNOPSIS
    gcloud beta ml speech operations COMMAND [GCLOUD_WIDE_FLAG ...]

DESCRIPTION
    (BETA) Get information about Google Cloud Speech long-running operations.

GCLOUD WIDE FLAGS
    These flags are available to all commands: --help.

    Run $ gcloud help for details.

COMMANDS
    COMMAND is one of the following:

     describe
        (BETA) Get description of a long-running speech recognition operation.

     wait
        (BETA) Poll long-running speech recognition operation until it
        completes.

NOTES
    This command is currently in beta and might change without notice. These
    variants are also available:

        $ gcloud ml speech operations

        $ gcloud alpha ml speech operations

